title: Refrigerator Power Cord Kit
description: Refrigerator Power Cord Kit ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 1 Review PartSelect Number PS358548 Manufacturer Part Number 4317824 Includes power cord and all necessary parts needed for complete installation of cord.

installationInstructions.author: Briant from Byron, MN
installationInstructions.title: There was no problem
installationInstructions.content: I simply had to hook up the power cord to the dishwasher so i could plug it into the outlet rather than direct wire the appliance.  Everything went very smoothly.  Everything needed for installation other than tools was provided.  Easy to follow instructions if you know a little about electrical wiring.
